OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,FMale detainees at an immigration
OL,7,Fcentre have been caught looking
OL,8,Fthrough the windows of women's
OL,9,Fbedrooms, a report has found.
OL,11,FFemale migrants at the centre have
OL,12,Fbeen unable to get around without a
OL,13,Fstaff escort, while men had free
OL,14,Fmovement, a report by the Chief
OL,15,FInspector of Prisons said.
