OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784002679
OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,FCharlie Taylor's report, which warned
OL,7,Fthat female asylum seekers are being
OL,8,Fput at risk of harm, found 43% of
OL,9,Fwomen at Dungavel immigration removal
OL,10,Fcentre in South Lanarkshire, Scotland,
OL,11,Ffeel unsafe in the outside areas.
OL,13,FAs of December 2025, 119 women were
OL,14,Fbeing held in immigration removal
OL,15,Fcentres and residential short-term
OL,16,Fholding facilities, according to Home
OL,17,FOffice figures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
