OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784002679
OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,FInspectors at Dungavel ` which holds
OL,7,Fboth men and women in separate units `
OL,8,Fwitnessed male detainees looking
OL,9,Fthrough women's bedroom windows and a
OL,10,Fgroup of men approached to ask why
OL,11,Fthey could not "mix with female
OL,12,Fdetainees", the report said.
OL,14,FThe centre also held a man assessed to
OL,15,Fpose a risk of harm to women at the
OL,16,Ftime of the inspection, and another
OL,17,Fwith impending prosecutions for sexual
OL,18,Foffences had been held there for over
OL,19,Fa year until shortly before, the
OL,20,Freport added.
OL,26,@sD@POUtD@JO]
