OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,F"Some women said they never left the
OL,7,Ffemale unit unless absolutely
OL,8,Fnecessary, while others were reluctant
OL,9,Feven when escorted," Mr Taylor's
OL,10,Freport said.
OL,12,FOne woman told inspectors: "We
OL,13,Fcan(not) go outside because of the
OL,14,Fmales and our time to do things are
OL,15,Fquick because of them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@TO]tD@\OUwD@WO]
