CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784002679
OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,FConcerns were first raised about
OL,7,FDungavel in 2021 when Mr Taylor warned
OL,8,Fthat female detainees were being
OL,9,Fforced to mix with men with a history
OL,10,Fof sexual violence because of Covid
OL,11,Frestrictions.
OL,13,FElsewhere in his report on women's
OL,14,Fexperience of immigration detention,
OL,15,FMr Taylor criticised staff for moving
OL,16,Fwomen across the country late at night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
