CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784002679
OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,FIn some cases, women who were
OL,7,Fpregnant, physically unwell or at risk
OL,8,Fof self-harm or suicide, were
OL,9,Ftransferred with "little regard for
OL,10,Ftheir health or the appropriateness of
OL,11,Fthe transfer", the report said.
OL,13,F"These journeys could be disruptive
OL,14,Fand exhausting and could further
OL,15,Fexacerbate existing health conditions.
OL,17,F"One woman described the process of
OL,18,Fbeing transferred as psychological
OL,19,Ftorture."
OL,26,@qD@ROUsD@MO]uD@AOUyD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
