PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784002679
OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,FInspectors also found "concerning
OL,7,Fpractices" around the use of
OL,8,Fhandcuffs, including the handcuffing
OL,9,Fof a pregnant woman.
OL,11,FMr Taylor said of his report: "Far
OL,12,Ffewer women than men are held in
OL,13,Fimmigration detention in the UK, and,
OL,14,Fas a result, their experiences are
OL,15,Fstill largely shaped by policies
OL,16,Fdesigned for men.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@JO]sD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
