OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784002679
OL,3,CMale migrant detainees caught looking
OL,4,Cinto women's bedrooms, report finds
OL,6,F"This report outlines where current
OL,7,Fprocesses fall short for women, but
OL,8,Falso what is working well. In the
OL,9,Ffacilities we visited for this review,
OL,10,Fwe found compassionate and committed
OL,11,Fstaff working hard to support a
OL,12,Fcomplex population.
OL,14,F"We hope our findings will help the
OL,15,FHome Office and its contractors
OL,16,Fcontinue to improve the support for
OL,17,Fthese very vulnerable detainees."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@aO]
